text: Daniel Robinson (born 3 July 1994) is a former professional Australian rules footballer who played for the Sydney Swans in the Australian Football League (AFL). Robinson was a NSW Scholarship selection at #51 in the 2013 rookie draft and was elevated to the senior list prior to the 2015 season. He made his senior debut against in round 9. Robinson requested a trade away from Sydney during the 2017 trade period in search of more opportunity.
